---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout pageTitle="Nuestra Iglesia">
  <main class="wrapper flex flex-col gap-3">
    <figure
      class="r-well w-full min-md:w-full aspect-square min-md:aspect-[16/9]"
    >
    </figure>
    <!-- Links importantes  -->
    <section>
      <article class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PsSIH1ixwti6Ix_zteCwB7WdPDf7ulqO/view?usp=sharing"
          target="_blank"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          class="bg-blue-800 text-white px-6 py-5 flex-1 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-950 flex items-center justify-between"
          >Confesión de Fe
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-file-symlink"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M4 21v-4a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3h5"></path><path d="M9 17l3 -3l-3 -3"
            ></path><path d="M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4"></path><path
              d="M5 11v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-9.5"
            ></path></svg
          ></a
        >
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AJi0h21EzAMjXlxQhWsumSXP4cL2-TRt/view?usp=share_link"
          target="_blank"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          class="bg-blue-800 text-white px-6 py-5 flex-1 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-950 flex items-center justify-between"
          >Nuestros Principios
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-file-symlink"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M4 21v-4a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3h5"></path><path d="M9 17l3 -3l-3 -3"
            ></path><path d="M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4"></path><path
              d="M5 11v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-9.5"
            ></path></svg
          ></a
        >
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1-l2aR8ls92op0SZWRsuxgc98--1Nca2C/view?usp=sharing"
          target="_blank"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
          class="bg-blue-800 text-white px-6 py-5 flex-1 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-950 flex items-center justify-between"
          >¿Qué valoramos?
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-file-symlink"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M4 21v-4a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3h5"></path><path d="M9 17l3 -3l-3 -3"
            ></path><path d="M14 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h4"></path><path
              d="M5 11v-6a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2h7l5 5v11a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-9.5"
            ></path></svg
          ></a
        >
      </article>
    </section>
    <!-- Mision y Vision -->
    <section
      class="mt-4 flex gap-6 flex-col text-center md:flex-row md:text-left"
    >
      <article class="r-well border border-zinc-300">
        <h4 class="text-2xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-contract"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M8 21h-2a3 3 0 0 1 -3 -3v-1h5.5"></path><path
              d="M17 8.5v-3.5a2 2 0 1 1 2 2h-2"></path><path
              d="M19 3h-11a3 3 0 0 0 -3 3v11"></path><path d="M9 7h4"
            ></path><path d="M9 11h4"></path><path
              d="M18.42 12.61a2.1 2.1 0 0 1 2.97 2.97l-6.39 6.42h-3v-3z"
            ></path></svg
          >Misión
        </h4>
        <p class="text-balance">
          Somos una comunidad cristiana de personas reconciliadas con Dios, y
          unos con otros, que reconocemos a Jesucristo, el Gran Pastor (Juan
          10), como nuestro único Señor y Salvador a quien amamos y obedecemos
          siendo y haciendo discípulos (Mateo 28:18-20, Lucas 10:27).
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="r-well border border-zinc-300">
        <h4 class="text-2xl mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="24"
            height="24"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-cross"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M10 21h4v-9h5v-4h-5v-5h-4v5h-5v4h5z"></path></svg
          >Visión
        </h4>
        <p class="text-blance">
          Queremos ser una familia que vive y disfruta el Evangelio de la Gracia
          de Cristo mientras reflejamos su Gloria y Belleza en nuestra ciudad.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
